232
00:12:16,893 --> 00:12:17,253
Certo.

233
00:12:17,812 --> 00:12:21,274
Vado.

234
00:12:21,374 --> 00:12:22,394
Elisa.

235
00:12:22,474 --> 00:12:25,073
Elisa, scusami.

236
00:12:27,595 --> 00:12:32,735
